{"article_id":"TypTBE7Tu0lDjLcL","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"After initially denying reports","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"suggesting","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"it had caused the crash of a Ukrainian airliner ,","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"Iran has acknowledged","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"that it `` unintentionally '' shot down the plane .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"The announcement on Saturday came","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"a day after officials from the United States , Canada and the United Kingdom said","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"they believed","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"the plane was accidentally brought down by an Iranian missile .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"The Ukraine International Airlines flight PS752","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"bound for Kyiv , Ukraine","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"crashed minutes after takeoff from the Imam Khomeini International Airport in Tehran on Wednesday ,","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"killing all 176 people on board .","depth":4},{"id":13,"text":"The crash happened","depth":3},{"id":14,"text":"hours after Iran launched missile attacks on US forces in Iraq in retaliation for the US assassination of top Iranian commander Qassem Soleimani .","depth":3},{"id":15,"text":"Here are all of the latest updates as of Saturday , January 11 :","depth":4},{"id":16,"text":"Truth about Iran crash could not be hidden :","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"Ukraine 's Zelenskyy","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"The findings by Ukrainian experts in Iran meant","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"that the truth about the crash could not be concealed ,","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelenskyy said in a televised address .","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"He also said","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"that he had agreed with Iran 's President Hassan Rouhani on the beginning of joint work to decode the black boxes of the Ukrainian plane","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"that was shot down this week .","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"He also urged Ukraine 's international partners to be united and persistent","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"until the investigation was complete .","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"Canadian Prime Minister Justin Trudeau told Iranian President Hassan Rouhani","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"that Canada wants `` full clarity '' on the plane crash ,","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"Trudeau said in a televised speech .","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"He added","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"that Iran did the right thing","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"by taking responsibility","depth":13},{"id":32,"text":"for downing the plane ,","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"calling it an important first step","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"and that it was necessary for Iran to compensate families of the victims .","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"President Rouhani , during a telephone conversation with Trudeau , promised further investigation into the downing of a Ukrainian passenger plane ,","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"Iranian state news agency IRNA reported .","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"`` Iran welcomes any international cooperation in the framework of international relations","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"to shed more light on the incident , ''","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"Rouhani said ,","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"promising further investigation into the crash","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"that","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"Tehran said","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"was caused by its air defences `` unintentionally '' .","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"The European Aviation Safety Agency","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"( EASA )","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"has urged all European airlines to avoid Iranian airspace `` until further notice '' in an expanded recommendation .","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"The advice expands on an earlier EASA recommendation","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"that national authorities bar airlines from overflying Iran below 25,000 feet .","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"It was issued `` in light of the statement from Iran","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"that its armed forces accidentally shot down a Ukrainian passenger aircraft , ''","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"EASA said .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelenskyy said","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"Iran 's acknowledgement","depth":13},{"id":54,"text":"that it shot down a Ukrainian passenger plane","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"was a step in the right direction","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"but wanted those responsible to be held to account .","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"`` I insist on immediately completing identification of the bodies and their return to Ukraine , ''","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"Zelenskyy wrote on Twitter","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"after speaking to Iranian President Rouhani .","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"Talked to @ HassanRouhani .","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"Acknowledging plane shot down","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"is a step in the right direction .","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"I insist on immediately completing identification of the bodies & their return to Ukraine .","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"The perpetrators must be held accountable .","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"We look forward to further legal & technical cooperation","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"- Володимир Зеленський","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"( @ ZelenskyyUa )","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"January 11 , 2020","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"Crowds of students in central Tehran protested after the government ' s response to the downing of the Ukrainian airliner ,","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"calling for those responsible to be held accountable .","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"Some of the protesters demanded","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"that Iran 's Supreme Leader Ayatollah Ali Khamenei step down .","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"`` Commander-in-chief","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"[ Khamenei ]","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"resign , resign , ''","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"videos","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"posted on Twitter","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"showed hundreds of people chanting in front of Tehran 's Amir Kabir university .","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"Speaking from Tehran ,","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"Dorsa Jibbari said :","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"`` There 's a lot of anger .","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"Iranians are demanding justice and accountability .","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"Many people ,","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"including families of the victims ,","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"do not understand","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"why their government would have lied to them for this long . ''","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"UK Prime Minister Boris Johnson has called Iran 's admission an `` important first step '' .","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"`` We will do everything","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"we can","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"to support the families of the four British victims","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"and ensure","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"they get the answers and the closure","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"they deserve , ''","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"he said in a statement","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"issued by his Downing Street office .","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"Johnson added","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"that the UK would work closely with Canada , Ukraine and other international partners","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"to ensure `` a comprehensive , transparent and independent international investigation and repatriation of those who died . ''","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"`` This tragic accident only reinforces the importance of de-escalating tensions in the region , ''","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"`` It is vital that all leaders now pursue a diplomatic way forward . '","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"' Iran 's downing of the plane was a `` terrible tragedy , ''","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"a senior Trump administration official told Reuters News Agency .","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"`` Ultimately , Iran made an awful mistake , ''","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"said the official ,","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"who spoke on the condition of anonymity .","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"`` Iran 's reckless actions have again had devastating consequences . ''","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"Ukrainian President Zelenskyy and French President Emmanuel Macron agreed on Saturday","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"that French specialists would help decode the black boxes of the Ukrainian plane","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"that crashed in Iran ,","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"according to Zelenskyy 's office .","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"Macron told Zelenskyy in a telephone call","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"that France had started a formal procedure","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"to launch an international investigation into the crash ,","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"Zelenskyy 's office said in a statement ,","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"adding","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"that Macron had agreed to visit Kyiv .","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"Hamid Baeidinejad , Iran 's ambassador to the UK , issued an apology","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"after denying reports","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"that his country might have been behind the passenger jet 's downing .","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"In my statement yesterday to the UK media , I conveyed the official findings of responsible authorities in my country","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"that missile could not be fired and hit the Ukrainian plane at that period of time .","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"I appologise and regret","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"for conveying such wrong findings .","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"- Hamid Baeidinejad","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"( @ baeidinejad )","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"January 11 , 2020","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"`` In my statement yesterday to the UK media , I conveyed the official findings of responsible authorities in my country","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"that missile could not be fired and hit the Ukrainian plane at that period of time , ''","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"Baeidinejad said in a tweet .","depth":8},{"id":131,"text":"Ukraine airline says","depth":5},{"id":132,"text":"plane had no warning of threat","depth":6},{"id":133,"text":"before Iran crash","depth":6},{"id":134,"text":"Ukraine International Airlines said","depth":7},{"id":135,"text":"its plane had received no warning from Tehran airport about a possible threat","depth":8},{"id":136,"text":"before it took off .","depth":8},{"id":137,"text":"At a briefing by its president and vice president , the airline also denied suggestions","depth":8},{"id":138,"text":"that the passenger plane had veered off its normal course ,","depth":8},{"id":139,"text":"and said","depth":8},{"id":140,"text":"the Iranian authorities should have closed the airport .","depth":8},{"id":141,"text":"Brigadier General Amir Ali Hajizadeh , a senior commander in the Islamic Revolutionary Guard Corps","depth":8},{"id":142,"text":"( IRGC ) ,","depth":8},{"id":143,"text":"said","depth":7},{"id":144,"text":"the Iranian missile operator","depth":10},{"id":145,"text":"who shot down the passenger jet","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"opened fire independently","depth":9},{"id":147,"text":"because of communications `` jamming '' .","depth":8},{"id":148,"text":"The operator had mistaken the Boeing 737 for a `` cruise missile ''","depth":9},{"id":149,"text":"and only had 10 seconds","depth":10},{"id":150,"text":"to decide","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"whether or not to open fire ,","depth":11},{"id":152,"text":"said Hajizadeh , the Guards ' aerospace commander , in televised remarks .","depth":8},{"id":153,"text":"Ukraine believes","depth":6},{"id":154,"text":"Iran plane probe will be 'objective and prompt '","depth":6},{"id":155,"text":"Ukraine said","depth":8},{"id":156,"text":"Iran had provided enough data","depth":10},{"id":157,"text":"including videos and photographs","depth":10},{"id":158,"text":"to show","depth":10},{"id":159,"text":"the investigation into Tehran 's downing of the passenger jet will be objective and prompt .","depth":10},{"id":160,"text":"President Zelenskyy 's office said","depth":8},{"id":161,"text":"Tehran provided Ukrainian experts in Iran `` with all the photos , videos and other materials ''","depth":10},{"id":162,"text":"linked to the investigation ,","depth":10},{"id":163,"text":"`` enough data","depth":10},{"id":164,"text":"to see","depth":11},{"id":165,"text":"that the investigation will be carried out objectively and promptly . ''","depth":11},{"id":166,"text":"A senior commander of Iran 's elite IRGC said","depth":8},{"id":167,"text":"he accepted full responsibility for the downing of the Ukrainian airliner .","depth":8},{"id":168,"text":"`` I take full responsibility","depth":10},{"id":169,"text":"and I will obey whatever decision is taken , ''","depth":10},{"id":170,"text":"Brigadier General Hajizadeh said in remarks","depth":10},{"id":171,"text":"broadcast on state television .","depth":10},{"id":172,"text":"`` I would prefer to die","depth":9},{"id":173,"text":"rather than witness such an incident . ''","depth":9},{"id":174,"text":"Canadian Prime Minister Justin Trudeau said","depth":8},{"id":175,"text":"his government sought a full investigation and full cooperation from the Iranian authorities .","depth":8},{"id":176,"text":"In a statement","depth":10},{"id":177,"text":"issued by his office ,","depth":10},{"id":178,"text":"Trudeau said","depth":9},{"id":179,"text":"Iran had now acknowledged","depth":9},{"id":180,"text":"that the plane was brought down by its own armed forces .","depth":9},{"id":181,"text":"`` Our focus remains closure , accountability , transparency , and justice for the families and loved ones of the victims .","depth":8},{"id":182,"text":"This is a national tragedy ,","depth":10},{"id":183,"text":"and all Canadians are mourning together , ''","depth":10},{"id":184,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":185,"text":"`` We will continue working with our partners around the world","depth":9},{"id":186,"text":"to ensure a complete and thorough investigation ,","depth":9},{"id":187,"text":"and the Canadian government expects full cooperation from Iranian authorities . ''","depth":8},{"id":188,"text":"Ukrainian President Zelenskyy said in a statement","depth":9},{"id":189,"text":"that Ukraine expected from Iran `` assurances '' of a `` full and open investigation ,","depth":10},{"id":190,"text":"bringing the perpetrators to justice '' .","depth":10},{"id":191,"text":"He added","depth":10},{"id":192,"text":"that Ukraine expected the `` paying of compensation '' and `` official apologies through diplomatic channels '' .","depth":10},{"id":193,"text":"He also expressed hope for the continuation of the crash investigation without delay .","depth":9},{"id":194,"text":"A team of Ukrainian investigators is in Iran .","depth":8},{"id":195,"text":"`` Our 45 specialists should get full access and cooperation","depth":10},{"id":196,"text":"to establish justice , ''","depth":10},{"id":197,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":198,"text":"The Ukrainian leader said","depth":7},{"id":199,"text":"he is due to hold a telephone call with Iranian President Hassan Rouhani later in the day .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":399,"left":214,"right":398,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":214,"left":212,"right":213,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":212,"left":208,"right":211,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":208,"left":204,"right":207,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":204,"left":202,"right":203,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":202,"left":0,"right":201,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":201,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":203,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":207,"left":5,"right":206,"relation":"same-unit","